manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Attention to Detail: Don't worry if you have kids since the design of this fabric drawer dresser is friendly to young ones. The anti-tip kit included provides a safe environment for your family, and fabric drawers won't pinch hands if little guys want to organize their clothing in drawers on their own. Hassle-Free Assembly: With a simple structure and assembly tools provided, you won’t need to spend your entire Sunday afternoon figuring out how to put it together. Simply follow the straightforward instructions, and you’ll have the storage unit nestled into its new home before you know it.

A Rustic Flair Besides the wooden top, the fabric drawer front is veneered with engineered wood in a rustic look, giving a classy and refined appeal. Anti-Tip Kit With an anti-tip kit included, you can mount the table to the wall and ensure a safe home for you and your family. Adjustable Feet 4 adjustable feet allow you to balance the nightstand on uneven ground and protect your floor from scratches.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are solid dressers...
reviews.reviewText: What I like is that these dressers are nice looking, they are easy to put together, they are solid and they are spacious. This is the fourth dresser I have purchased from this seller. I have two of the double wide dressers and two of the tall ones. I love all of them. They fit right in with my other rustic brown and black furniture. Look, if you put these together the right way, they will be solid pieces of furniture that will last a long time. I'm a woman and I'm disabled and I put all of them together myself. It's so easy. Just follow the instructions and get all of the hardware organized and you need a small screw driver (not included) and not listed, but it's for the drawer pulls. It just makes it easier to get them tightened.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ten Star! Just as described!
reviews.reviewText: Purchased - Color: White. After purchasing two others and having to return both for missing parts, bent parts, etc, finally found a winner with the Songmics product. Yes, it's a small storage cabinet - just as described, and what I was looking for. Yes, the drawers are made from fabric, just as described - the same type of materials as a storage cube. Don't expect it to hold a bowling ball! This is for clothing items. It is extremely easy to assemble, it is exactly as described in size and produce description; it took me less than 45 minutes to assemble two of these. Very intuitive to assemble. These cabinets will be used in the interior of a closet, to fit under clothing rack. They will not be used for heavy items. So happy that I went with this brand! I may change out the tiny knobs on each drawer and figure out a way to strengthen the back side of the pull front to add some support. These may cause a bit more, but are by far worth it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 3, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice Dresser for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I was looking for a small dresser to use as a tv stand and light storage. This dresser is exactly what I needed. lightweight and easy to assemble.The instructions were easy to follow, I did make one mistake though when I installed the middle stand for the drawers I had it backwards. but it was an easy fix, just 4 screws and flip. All screws and tools provided except a phillips screwdriver.The "wood" has a nice look. The metal frame is strong enough to hold a 40in tv(approx. 50 pds.) The cloth drawer has a hard bottom you install and can hold light stuff like socks and underwear. but I would not put anything heavy.The only downside I can see is that the sides are open and you can see the sides of the cloth drawer on both sides. It would be nice to have a couple "wood" sides to complete the full "wood" look.I am happy with the purchase an would buy similar again. But if you are looking for real wood or something to hold heavy object or in bulk, i would get something else.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars ok for kids, not adults and definitely NOT worth $85. READ THE DIMENSIONS
reviews.reviewText: This is super super small. I am 5ft 5in and this comes up to about mid-thigh. The drawers are small, you can't fit much. If you are a very petit person or a child this would maybe work, or as toy storage. It was purchased for an adult who is 5ft 10in and slim, he can fit about 2 pairs of jeans in one drawer. I regret my purchase because I unfortunately didn't read the dimensions beforehand which is something I usually do, but I assumed it would be comparable to one I purchased before. You can get much larger fabric dressers for less or around the same price. I purchased a Sorbus one about a year ago for my room that is the same size as a regular dresser with deep drawers and it was around the same price as this. I am probably going to paint the drawer fronts and use it for my child and get a Sorbus one for the adult instead.

reviews.reviewTitle: Needed something inexpensive for the spare room
reviews.reviewText: I recently snagged this SONGMICS Dresser for the spare bedroom, and it's been a solid addition. Now, it's not a big dresser, but that's exactly what I was looking for. It fits perfectly without taking up too much space, and the size is just right for the room. The design is a mix of wood and cloth drawers, which I wasn't sure about at first, but turns out, they're pretty sturdy and look decent too.The drawers themselves are more spacious than I expected. They hold all the extra stuff we have without any hassle. And the top of the dresser? It's solid enough to hold the TV, which is a big plus. I was a bit concerned about the weight, but it's been holding up just fine.Assembling it was a piece of cake. Didn't take too long, and the instructions were clear enough. It's not the kind of furniture that'll make you pull your hair out trying to put it together, which is always a relief.For anyone looking for a practical, no-fuss dresser for a smaller room or a spare bedroom, this SONGMICS dresser is a good pick. It does the job, looks pretty neat, and doesn't hit your wallet too hard. Plus, it's versatile enough to double as a TV stand, which is a nice bonus.
